name: Sachary Jeffington
content: Sachary Jeffington was a human female who was elected as President of the planet Dalna around 230 BBY. She was secretly allied with the Nihil pirates and the Tempest commanded by Tempest Runner Kara Xoo. Originally hailing from offworld, Jeffington's election was a surprise to the Dalnan population as no one knew her particularly well. When Jedi Knight Vernestra Rwoh visited Dalna investigating Nihil activity, she found Jeffington incredibly frustrating upon finally getting a chance to speak with her, as Jeffington cared more about the gnostra bushes which were Dalna's primary source of income. A farmer, Jeffington had pale skin and wore homespun clothing.
